{
  "name": "twind",
  "version": "1.0.0-next.2",
  "description": "tailwindcss compat based on twind",
  "homepage": "https://twind.dev",
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/tw-in-js/twind/issues"
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git+https://github.com/tw-in-js/twind.git",
    "directory": "packages/twind"
  },
  "keywords": [
    "twind",
    "tw-in-js",
    "tailwind",
    "tailwindcss",
    "tailwind-in-js"
  ],
  "license": "MIT",
  "author": {
    "name": "Sascha Tandel",
    "url": "https://github.com/sastan"
  },
  "engines": {
    "node": ">=12.4"
  },
  "publishConfig": {
    "tag": "next",
    "access": "public",
    "directory": "dist"
  },
  "contributors": [
    {
      "name": "Luke Jackson",
      "url": "lukejacksonn.github.io"
    },
    {
      "name": "Sascha Tandel",
      "url": "https://github.com/sastan"
    }
  ],
  "type": "module",
  "main": "./twind.cjs",
  "exports": {
    ".": {
      "esnext": "./twind.esnext.js",
      "module": "./twind.js",
      "script": "./twind.umd.js",
      "types": "./twind.d.ts",
      "node": {
        "module": "./twind.js",
        "import": "./twind.mjs",
        "require": "./twind.cjs"
      },
      "default": "./twind.js"
    },
    "./package.json": "./package.json",
    "./colors": {
      "esnext": "./colors.esnext.js",
      "module": "./colors.js",
      "script": "./colors.umd.js",
      "types": "./colors.d.ts",
      "node": {
        "module": "./colors.js",
        "import": "./colors.mjs",
        "require": "./colors.cjs"
      },
      "default": "./colors.js"
    }
  },
  "sideEffects": true,
  "dependencies": {
    "@twind/core": "*",
    "@twind/preset-autoprefix": "*",
    "@twind/preset-tailwind": "*"
  },
  "peerDependencies": {
    "typescript": "^4.4.0"
  },
  "peerDependenciesMeta": {
    "typescript": {
      "optional": true
    }
  },
  "module": "./twind.js",
  "esnext": "./twind.esnext.js",
  "unpkg": "./twind.umd.js",
  "jsdelivr": "./twind.umd.js",
  "umd:main": "./twind.umd.js",
  "types": "./twind.d.ts",
  "readme": "# twind\n\n---\n\n## READ THIS FIRST!\n\n**Twind v1 is still in beta. Expect bugs!**\n\nTwind v1 is a complete rewrite aiming to be compatible with Tailwind v3 classes\n\n---\n\n## Installation\n\nInstall from npm:\n\n```sh\n# Using npm\nnpm install twind@next\n\n# Using Yarn\nyarn add twind@next\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```js\nimport 'twind'\n```\n\nOr using a CDNs:\n\n```html\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/twind@next\"></script>\n```\n"
}